  "body": "<img alt=\"6a-IMG_3624.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309054745-MS2SD9RC551QUSCZD66E/6a-IMG_3624.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"6b-IMG_1962.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309052158-LFBJVO7UQ7WV2PWL9VT1/6b-IMG_1962.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6c-IMG_1966.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309055109-LZQBW8JBIPDSKKK6I6ZQ/6c-IMG_1966.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6d-IMG_1965.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309055983-8V2ARLAIMXI7CELO2UAO/6d-IMG_1965.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6e-IMG_1971.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309056284-2WACZRI3O98GROJLMXSY/6e-IMG_1971.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6f-IMG_1974.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309095648-TMBHQM7TP1Z3TH5PAYZ4/6f-IMG_1974.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6g-IMG_1978.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309095566-168JY2R8MXI3YVXHBXQ5/6g-IMG_1978.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6h-IMG_1967.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598309097170-LN1D2NHN9PO9V6Q5SNRZ/6h-IMG_1967.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>While in Florida, I saw my ball garland for the first time at <a href=\"http://whimsodoodle.com/\">Whim So Doodle</a>. I got excited and had to take some cheesy photos. I also had to get it so I could come home and freshen up my desk area.I gathered together a bunch of items, mostly from my <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=stitched&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fsearch%2Easpx%3FKeywords%3Damy%2Btangerine%2Bstitched%2B2014\">Stitched</a> collection. Though the set up was looking good, it was time to change it up a little bit.The felt garland is available online <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=33086&amp;m=7429&amp;afftrack=garland&amp;urllink=store%2Escrapbook%2Ecom%2Fac%2D368979%2Ehtml\">here</a> and <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=garland&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fproduct%2Easpx%3Fid%3D312644\">here</a>.</p><p>What have you created from <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=stitched&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fsearch%2Easpx%3FKeywords%3Damy%2Btangerine%2Bstitched%2B2014\">Stitched</a> other than paper projects?</p>"
